imdb.plot outline: JENNY is a down to earth girl who always wore her heart on her sleeve. She never realized how worn out she would feel being so vulnerable and letting herself fall in love with her best friend JEFF. She quickly realizes she doesn't have the time to waste and spills her heart out. JEFF has kept his love for her a secret for so long he can't help but to finally give in and let JENNY into his heart. We follow their love transform from passive hellos to romantic moments through flashbacks in what feels like a lifetime of memories. With the help of their friends CYNTHIA, GARY and RICK we're taken on a hilarious roller coaster of teenage love.
